gujarati.context:
Joy of the generous, joy of the limitless; 
Unexpressed form's joy, infinite's joy too; 
Eternal joy of selfless desires, harmonious joy too.

Here is the translation:

Joy of Hari's bliss, joy of divine love, I will learn;
Bliss of earthy bliss, bliss of worldly delight, I will know; Bliss of brotherly bliss, bliss of eternal bliss, I will see; Guru's guidance, I will accomplish.

Joy of good karma is the joy of the year, bliss; 
Joy of self-knowledge is so; 
Joy of having a thousand heads is joy of the assembly, all-encompassing knowledge is seen.

Peacefulness is delightful, being pleased; 
Pleasure of a thousand things is that; 
Desired state is desirable, truth process that.
